value.name: The Four of Them
value.overview: Getting crushed by your crush. Coming out to your parents. Learning that your sister is your biggest dating rival. High school sure does have its share of twists & moments of drama. To get through it all with your sanity intact, you’re going to need some really good friends. Friends like Johnny, Mariel, and Gaby who, one way or another, will find a way to get through their teenage years together.
